    "For instance, Ope-nAI (https://openai.com/blog/introducing-superalignment), the creator of ChatGPT, has announced that they are going to leverage 20% of computing resources to fine-tune strong pretrained LLMs for regularizing LLMs to faithfully follow instructions or generate safe outputs.",
